data.description: Stunning townhome offering modern living with fantastic amenities and water views. Here's your chance to own the nicest and updated unit in the community. First floor is ceramic tile, second floor is laminate, freshly painted. You will fall in love with this 3 BR/2.5 bath 1 car garage beautifully upgraded town home, in the resort style Colony Reserve at Lake Worth community. Just bring your toothbrush! Great location about 15 minutes from beautiful beaches, near shopping and great dining. Don't miss out on this opportunity.
